<body><bold>Chitin Helmet<end>
<tab><RECIPE name=chitinHelmet domain=Hivetera>
Nomads fear the night, as this is when the undead rise under the waxing moon. To protect their heads during fights with these enemies, they were able to build a helmet using Chitin Plates. It is said that there once was a clan of nomads running around in nothing but helmets.

